title: Stargate Universe Kino Webisodes 720p The Definitive Collection
description:
This is a collection of all 34 Kino webisodes released during the broadcast of Stargate Universe.

Most were sourced from the season one blu ray; of thos, many were only available at a resolution of 480 pixels, a few (such as Wait For It and Horrible Accident which is shown above) were full HD 1920 x 1080p. A small number are taken from the originally downloaded files and have been upscaled.

The webisodes are now all 1280 x 720p with stereo sound. The files are mp4 with aac audio.

The subtitles are English SRT files.

Enjoy and please seed.
